    <link href="/2025/10/05/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <url>/2025/10/05/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h5 id="1、矩阵的迹的性质"><a href="#1、矩阵的迹的性质" class="headerlink" title="1、矩阵的迹的性质"></a>1、矩阵的迹的性质</h5><blockquote><ul><li>线性算子</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\operatorname{tr}(A+B) = \operatorname{tr}(A) + \operatorname{tr}(B), \quad \operatorname{tr}(cA) = c \operatorname{tr}(A)</script><ul><li>转置不变性</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\operatorname{tr}(A)=\operatorname{tr}(A^{T})</script><ul><li>共轭转置</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">tr(A^{H})=\overline{tr(A)}</script><ul><li>循环性质</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">tr(AB)=tr(BA) \\tr(ABC)=tr(CAB)=tr(BCA)</script><ul><li>项式不变性</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">B=P^{-1}AP  \Rightarrow tr(A)=tr(B)</script><ul><li>特征值之和等于迹</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">tr(A)=\sum_{i=1}^{n}\lambda_{i}</script><ul><li>迹与 Frobenius 范数</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\|\mathbf{A}\|_{F}^{2} = \sum_{i=1}^{m}\sum_{j=1}^{n} |a_{ij}|^{2} = \operatorname{tr}(\mathbf{A}^{H}\mathbf{A}) = \operatorname{tr}(\mathbf{A}\mathbf{A}^{H})</script><ul><li>迹与行列式</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">det(e^{A})=e^{tr(A)}</script><ul><li>迹与导数</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\frac{\partial{ {tr}(AB)} }{\partial{A}}=B^{T}</script></blockquote><h5 id="2、在复数域上使用施密特正交化时的内积与实数域不同"><a href="#2、在复数域上使用施密特正交化时的内积与实数域不同" class="headerlink" title="2、在复数域上使用施密特正交化时的内积与实数域不同"></a>2、在复数域上使用施密特正交化时的内积与实数域不同</h5><blockquote><ul><li>实数域</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\langle x,y\rangle \triangleq x^{\mathrm{T}}y=\sum_{i=1}^{n}x_{i}y_{i}</script><ul><li>复数域</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\langle x,y\rangle \triangleq x^{\mathrm{T}}y=\sum_{i=1}^{n}x_{i}\overline{y_{i}}</script></blockquote><h5 id="3、柯西施瓦兹不等式的三种形式"><a href="#3、柯西施瓦兹不等式的三种形式" class="headerlink" title="3、柯西施瓦兹不等式的三种形式"></a>3、柯西施瓦兹不等式的三种形式</h5><blockquote><ul><li>代数形式</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\left( \sum_{i=1}^{n}a_ib_i \right)^2 \le \left( \sum_{i=1}^{n}a_i^2 \right) \left( \sum_{i=1}^{n}b_i^2 \right)</script><ul><li>向量形式</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\left| ab \right| \le \left| a \right|\left| b \right|</script><ul><li>积分形式</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\left( \int_a^b f(x)g(x)dx\right)^2 = \left( \int_a^b f(x)^2dx \right)\left( \int_a^b g(x)^2dx \right)</script><p><strong>注：柯西施瓦兹不等式对于广义的内积空间同样适用</strong></p></blockquote><h5 id="4、-Taylor-展开式大全"><a href="#4、-Taylor-展开式大全" class="headerlink" title="4、$Taylor$展开式大全"></a>4、$Taylor$展开式大全</h5><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{align*}e^{x} &= \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{x^{n}}{n !} = 1+x+\frac{x^{2}}{2 !}+\cdots+\frac{x^{n}}{n !}+\cdots, \quad x \in(-\infty,+\infty) \\[1.5ex]\sin x &= \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{(-1)^{n}}{(2 n+1) !} x^{2 n+1} = x-\frac{x^{3}}{3 !}+\frac{x^{5}}{5 !}-\cdots+\frac{(-1)^{n}}{(2 n+1) !} x^{2 n+1}+\cdots, \quad x \in(-\infty,+\infty) \\[1.5ex]\cos x &= \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{(-1)^{n}}{(2 n) !} x^{2 n} = 1-\frac{x^{2}}{2 !}+\frac{x^{4}}{4 !}-\cdots+\frac{(-1)^{n}}{(2 n) !} x^{2 n}+\cdots, \quad x \in(-\infty,+\infty) \\[1.5ex]\ln(1+x) &= \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{(-1)^{n}}{n+1} x^{n+1} = x-\frac{x^{2}}{2}+\frac{x^{3}}{3}-\cdots+\frac{(-1)^{n}}{n+1} x^{n+1}+\cdots, \quad x \in (-1,1] \\[1.5ex]\frac{1}{1-x} &= \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} x^{n} = 1+x+x^{2}+\cdots+x^{n}+\cdots, \quad x \in(-1,1) \\[1.5ex]\frac{1}{1+x} &= \sum_{n=0}^{\infty}(-1)^{n} x^{n} = 1-x+x^{2}-\cdots+(-1)^{n} x^{n}+\cdots, \quad x \in(-1,1) \\[1.5ex](1+x)^{\alpha} &= 1+\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{\alpha(\alpha-1) \cdots(\alpha-n+1)}{n !} x^{n} \\&= 1+\alpha x+\frac{\alpha(\alpha-1)}{2 !}x^{2}+\cdots+\frac{\alpha(\alpha-1) \cdots(\alpha-n+1)}{n !} x^{n}+\cdots, \quad x \in(-1,1) \\[1.5ex]\arctan x &= \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{(-1)^{n}}{2 n+1} x^{2 n+1} = x-\frac{x^{3}}{3}+\frac{x^{5}}{5}-\cdots+\frac{(-1)^{n}}{2 n+1} x^{2 n+1}+\cdots, \quad x \in[-1,1] \\[1.5ex]\arcsin x &= \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{(2 n) !}{4^{n}(n !)^{2}(2 n+1)} x^{2 n+1} \\&= x+\frac{1}{6} x^{3}+\frac{3}{40} x^{5}+\frac{5}{112} x^{7}+\cdots+\frac{(2 n) !}{4^{n}(n !)^{2}(2 n+1)} x^{2 n+1}+\cdots, \quad x \in[-1,1] \\[1.5ex]\tan x &= \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{B_{2 n}(-4)^{n}(1-4^{n})}{(2 n) !} x^{2 n-1} \\&= x+\frac{1}{3} x^{3}+\frac{2}{15} x^{5}+\frac{17}{315} x^{7}+\cdots, \quad x \in(-\pi/2, \pi/2)\end{align*}</script><p><strong>注：</strong>$(1+x)^{\alpha}$的收敛域与$\alpha$有关,但收敛半径都是$1$,具体收敛域如下：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{cases} x \in (-1,1),  & \text{if } \alpha \leq -1 \\x \in (-1,1], & \text{if } -1 < \alpha < 0 \\x \in [-1,1],  & \text{if } \alpha > 0 \end{cases}</script></blockquote><h5 id="5、"><a href="#5、" class="headerlink" title="5、"></a>5、</h5>]]></content>
    
    
    
